{"tid":2036319,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「呃人文宣就係咁賤」 - 馮睎乾","createTime":"2020-05-26T11:29:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T11:57:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"61e544701a1745ec695c6e8d82b7c761851150a5","tid":2036319,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T11:29:54.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20200526/20924534/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200526%2F20924534%2F&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMA60J0iXDlbDdnmyxhWT3nOs%3D&h=b4f45e9d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200526%2F20924534%2F&h=b630c670\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20200526/20924534/</a><br />\n<br />\n「呃人文宣就係咁賤」 - 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200526/large/1590398357_d7d7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200526%2Flarge%2F1590398357_d7d7.jpg&h=6a100f57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n5月24日下午，。。。。。。。。。。必然發生在14:05之前。<br />\n<br />\n香港法律第210章《盜竊罪條例》第18C的「不付款而離去」說：。。。。。。。。。。。防暴警盜竊的表證都成立。<br />\n<br />\n犯了法，。。。。。。。。。。在一些接受高等教育的知識分子及專業人士身上都沒有。」<br />\n<br />\n然而警方選擇包庇該名疑犯，只在Facebook發聲明：「警方已經向店舖付清相關樽裝飲品的費用。」聲明時間是15:47。專頁「PSHK」也在16:08上載影片，清楚顯示三個穿藍色背心的公共關係科警員到便利店補鑊付款。由14:05到15:47，證明是在盜竊案發生近兩小時後才付款，而付款者是三名藍衣警員。這種「後數」方式，智力正常者都知道是犯法的。<br />\n<br />\n本來真相大白，卻有一個「向香港警察致敬」專頁，在19:01發佈影片，題為「黃屍又再次利用剪輯技巧誣蔑警方盜竊」，內容跟「飛影」一樣，但刻意配上欺騙觀眾的字幕，例如鏡頭只見另一個警員（並非穿藍背心）進來向店員索水，字幕卻打上「30秒後安排有銀包便衣俾錢」。這專頁散播假資訊，鐵證如山，我呼籲各位舉報。<br />\n<br />\n可笑的是，我見到一名標榜理性的藍絲「網友」，為證明黃絲說謊，四處轉載「向香港警察致敬」那段只有弱智人士才相信的影片，還大言不慚批評黃媒「呃人文宣就係咁賤」。警察為什麼有恃無恐？真要多謝這些又蠢又賤的藍絲了。 <br />\n<br />\n馮睎乾<br />\n電郵 :philomusus@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n精挑細味 籽想好食，即like「籽想好食」FB專頁！"},{"pid":"8e08c121214d14d677be3161260abfbf17bd93c7","tid":2036319,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T11:39:52.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fbe590c3333899b5c4a6daa9cbb6719242e84cb","tid":2036319,"uid":95221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T11:41:09.000Z","msg":"咁撚On9"},{"pid":"1b99250c8d15ef02644622c750a9a2c1a7204269","tid":2036319,"uid":147952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T11:42:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同温層</span>"},{"pid":"2e3bcb0da806b4a6cab2ce207273645a2d16a178","tid":2036319,"uid":29726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T11:57:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}